    Title: Young India
    Editor: M. K. Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 1 March 1929
---
If you would ask Him to help you, you would go to Him in all your nakedness,
approach Him without reservations, also without fear or doubts as to how
He can help a fallen being like you. He who has helped millions who have
approached Him, is He going to desert you?
